snippet.title: Tales of Carmelot Fast Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Play it here: http://snapbreak.com/puzzle/tales-of-carmelot

Welcome to the magical kingdom of Carmelot.
Join Ryan O'brien in his quest of finding the kingdom's missing pot of gold.
